# .dockerignore - Exclude files from Docker build context
#
# This file minimizes the Docker build context size by excluding
# unnecessary files and directories from being sent to the Docker daemon.
#
# Benefits:
#   - Faster builds (less data to copy)
#   - Smaller build context
#   - Better layer caching
#   - Avoid accidentally including secrets

